originalSql:
SELECT 
    a.name AS actor_name, 
    t.title AS movie_title, 
    c.kind AS cast_type, 
    m.info AS movie_info, 
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT k.keyword, ', ') AS keywords
FROM 
    aka_name a
JOIN 
    cast_info ci ON a.person_id = ci.person_id
JOIN 
    title t ON ci.movie_id = t.id
JOIN 
    comp_cast_type c ON ci.person_role_id = c.id
JOIN 
    movie_info m ON t.id = m.movie_id
LEFT JOIN 
    movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id
LEFT JOIN 
    keyword k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id
WHERE 
    m.info_type_id IN (SELECT id FROM info_type WHERE info LIKE 'budget')
    AND t.production_year > 2000
GROUP BY 
    a.name, t.title, c.kind, m.info
ORDER BY 
    COUNT(DISTINCT k.id) DESC, a.name

SELECT COALESCE("t6"."ACTOR_NAME", "t6"."ACTOR_NAME") AS "ACTOR_NAME", "t6"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t6"."CAST_TYPE", "t6"."MOVIE_INFO", "t6"."KEYWORDS", "t6"."EXPR$5" AS "FD_COL_5", "t6"."name"
FROM (SELECT MIN("aka_name"."name") AS "ACTOR_NAME", MIN("title"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", MIN("comp_cast_type"."kind") AS "CAST_TYPE", MIN("s1"."info") AS "MOVIE_INFO", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "keyword"."keyword", ', ') AS "KEYWORDS", COUNT(DISTINCT "keyword"."id") AS "EXPR$5", "aka_name"."name"
FROM "aka_name"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "title" ON "cast_info"."movie_id" = "title"."id"
INNER JOIN "comp_cast_type" ON "cast_info"."person_role_id" = "comp_cast_type"."id"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "title"."id" = "s1"."movie_id"
LEFT JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "title"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"
LEFT JOIN "keyword" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"
WHERE "s1"."info_type_id" IN (SELECT "id" AS "ID"
FROM "info_type"
WHERE "info" LIKE 'budget') AND "title"."production_year" > 2000
GROUP BY "aka_name"."name", "title"."title", "comp_cast_type"."kind", "s1"."info"
ORDER BY 6 DESC NULLS FIRST, "aka_name"."name") AS "t6"
